!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Digital Marketing Portfolio</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}

body {
  background: #0b0f1a;
  color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  background: rgba(11,15,26,0.9);
  padding: 15px 40px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  z-index: 1000;
}

header h1 {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #00e5ff;
}

nav a {
  color: #fff;
  margin-left: 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

nav a:hover {
  color: #00e5ff;
}.hero {
  height: 90vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #13203a, #0b0f1a);
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 42px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.hero p {
  max-width: 600px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.buttons {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.btn {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  margin: 5px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: #00e5ff;
  color: #000;
}

.btn-outline {
  border: 1px solid #00e5ff;
  background: transparent;
  color: #00e5ff;
}

section {
  padding: 60px 10%;
}
.hero {
  height: 90vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #13203a, #0b0f1a);
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 42px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.hero p {
  max-width: 600px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.buttons {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.btn {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  margin: 5px;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: #00e5ff;
  color: #000;
}

.btn-outline {
  border: 1px solid #00e5ff;
  background: transparent;
  color: #00e5ff;
}

section {
  padding: 60px 10%;
}
h3 {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: #00e5ff;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}

.card {
  background: #121a2b;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.stats {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.stat {
  text-align: center;
  margin: 20px;
}

.stat h2 {
  color: #00e5ff;
  font-size: 32px;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  background: #0a0e18;
  font-size: 14px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

input, textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  margin: 10px 0;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

textarea {
  height: 120px;
}
form button {
  background: #00e5ff;
  border: none;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Digital Marketer</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
    <a href="#stats">Results</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Driving Growth Through Digital Marketing</h2>
  <p>I help businesses grow with SEO, PPC, social media marketing, and conversion optimization strategies that deliver real results.</p>
  <div class="buttons">
    <button class="btn btn-primary">View Portfolio</button>
    <button class="btn btn-outline">Contact Me</button>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <h3>About Me</h3>
  <p>
    I am a Digital Marketing Specialist with expertise in building data-driven marketing campaigns that increase traffic,
    generate leads, and maximize ROI. I work with startups and established brands to scale their online presence.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="services">
  <h3>Services</h3>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">SEO Optimization</div>
    <div class="card">Google Ads & PPC</div>
    <div class="card">Social Media Marketing</div>
    <div class="card">Content Marketing</div>
    <div class="card">Email Marketing</div>
    <div class="card">Marketing Analytics</div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="portfolio">
  <h3>Portfolio</h3>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>E-commerce Brand</h4>
      <p>Increased organic traffic by 250% using SEO strategy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Tech Startup</h4>
      <p>Generated 5x ROAS through Google Ads campaigns.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Fashion Brand</h4>
      <p>Boosted social engagement by 320% in 3 months.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="stats">
  <h3>Results</h3>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>120+</h2>
      <p>Campaigns</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>5M+</h2>
      <p>Leads Generated</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <h2>8x</h2>
      <p>Average ROI</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h3>Contact Me</h3>
  <form>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
    <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
    <textarea placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
    <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
  </form>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Digital Marketing Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>